#dogearmy #doge #dogetothemoon

All the things you read about #dogecoin in today's social media and news is exactly what they said about $BIT in the beginning. $DOGE is in fact inevitable. They just are just unwilling to see that  #dogeisthefuture

@Dogecoinrich Sky's the limit. All depends on what people are willing to buy 1 doge for.  The question you should ask is. Why can't #DOGE be $100, $500 or maybe even $1000. We already know companies will pay big money for bitcoin and ethereum. #dogecoin can definitely be the same. HODL!!!
